{"tid":1256624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會選舉確認書DQ候選人 625諮詢","createTime":"2019-06-25T06:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:28:20.000Z","uid":247725,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a03547e72163da59d74dfa8c90e6d4483ad7457","tid":1256624,"uid":247725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"過左的話 選舉主任可以DQ候選人入閘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年6月25日<br />\n時間：晚上7時至9時<br />\n地點：鰂魚涌基利路1號鰂魚涌社區會堂<br />\n「區議會選舉活動建議指引」全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/31OUllu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31OUllu&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443vYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=4a066917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/31OUllu</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1069457753259477&amp;id=463135367225055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1069457753259477%26id%3D463135367225055&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443vYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=82ea7092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1069457753259477&amp;id=463135367225055</a>"},{"pid":"9196047e09aff96d91f375eac0f48e7b538e1d7a","tid":1256624,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:21:43.000Z","msg":"取消左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e525c1db7b5c04032583b5b3e7ba2df32a54ece","tid":1256624,"uid":969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"取消左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚到咁"},{"pid":"3e69b385236343ccf2d76ab4a268adb0e43f3350","tid":1256624,"uid":247725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"Oh 剛剛now 新聞話今晚諮詢取消了"},{"pid":"4b711f5a7580b80bdb1f3b656b2dd98964682c93","tid":1256624,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"攪錯呀<br />\n乜理由要取消呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8bc23f68d88a034ad83863c1e06c849328e4a6","tid":1256624,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"衝出黎比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9361b2194e993d4c76100d75d4afd6cd4964dbe","tid":1256624,"uid":127807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:02:12.000Z","msg":"【區選佈陣】民主派籲限期前表態反對確認書：炸爆選管會電郵<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190703/59785123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785123&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443vYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=08c47a0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785123&h=db1cbf22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190703/59785123</a><br />\n<br />\n區議會換屆選舉將於11月24日舉行，選管會早前發表區議會選舉活動建議指引，建議在區選中引入「確認書」制度，要求參選人簽署聲明擁護《基本法》及保證效忠香港特別行政區，諮詢期本月10日屆滿。民主派議員批評政府利用確認書DQ參選人，剝削選舉權利，呼籲市民以提意見促選管會撤銷「確認書」。"},{"pid":"28e99d7e85d28471e99d480f1cd62a8ed86dafce","tid":1256624,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6659f6ae1f5c352a1816985ea99e2c5723748797","tid":1256624,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb3a5973d52c8933463912c5e820fdcb4883714","tid":1256624,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2576488119051989?s=575092502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F2576488119051989%3Fs%3D575092502&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV44